{"title":"小明系列 I","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-3136","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>这是伟大的小明系列的第一题！！！当当当当！华丽出场啦！！！</p>\n<p>这是一道很简单的题目（原因是小明刚出场！！！）</p>\n<p>小明请你帮他打印出一个矩阵(如下)</p>\n<p>1 2 4</p>\n<p>3 5</p>\n<p>6</p>\n<p>这是一个三阶的</p>\n<p>请你打印出N阶的（1&lt;=N&lt;=20）</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>一个整数N</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个N阶三角矩阵</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>4</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1 2 4 7</p>\n<p>3 5 8</p>\n<p>6 9</p>\n<p>10</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>每两个数之间有个空格就行了（小明要求很低！）</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}